.TH TA 1 "2026-07-03" "Heirloom Darwin port" "Document Processing Tools"
.SH NAME
ta \- convert Adobe font metrics to the troff font-table format
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ta
.I "AFM-file"
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B ta
reads an Adobe Font Metrics (AFM) file and writes the
device-independent troff font-description table on standard
output. The output is suitable for use by
.BR troff (1)
and by
.BR dpost (1)
when installing new PostScript fonts.
.SH HEIRLOOM DARWIN PORT
Supports the shared modality flags. See
.BR heirloom-modality (7).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR troff (1),
.BR dpost (1),
.BR afmtodit (1).
